{
  "id": "5e7d85973a77c100178317bf",
  "title": "湖とコップのたとえ",
  "created": 1585284522,
  "updated": 1676535460,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5e7d85973a77c100178317bf",
      "text": "湖とコップのたとえ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284522,
      "updated": 1585284527
    },
    {
      "id": "620d1727aff09e0000a6f97f",
      "text": "「湖にコップ一杯の水を入れたとする。水面が上がらないと言えば誤りであり、上がると言えば愚かである」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1645025063,
      "updated": 1645025064
    },
    {
      "id": "620d1727aff09e0000a6f980",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1645025063,
      "updated": 1645025063
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d85afaff09e00009d2c24",
      "text": "「湖にコップ一杯の水を入れた。水面は上がるか？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284527,
      "updated": 1585284565
    },
    {
      "id": "5edb6f97aff09e0000cc9642",
      "text": "　という記述を何かで読んだ記憶があるのだけど元ネタなんだっけ？？見つけられてない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591439256,
      "updated": 1676535351
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d85d5aff09e00009d2c26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284565,
      "updated": 1585284565
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d85f2aff09e00009d2c27",
      "text": "「上がるか、上がらないか」という二者択一の問いにすると、論理的にはどちらかが正しくてどちらかが誤りなので、正しい方を選ぶことを重要だと思い込んでしまう。 #誤った二者択一",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284595,
      "updated": 1626551633
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d8662aff09e00009d2c28",
      "text": "しかし現実社会の問いでは、しばしば「どちらであっても大差ない」ことがある。この場合、正解がどちらであるか知ることに有用性がない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284706,
      "updated": 1585284832
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d86e1aff09e00009d2c29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284834,
      "updated": 1585284834
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d86e1aff09e00009d2c2a",
      "text": "[たとえ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284834,
      "updated": 1585284840
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d85b4aff09e00009d2c25",
      "text": "[有用性と正しさ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284532,
      "updated": 1585284853
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d86eeaff09e00009d2c2b",
      "text": "[有用性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284846,
      "updated": 1585284878
    },
    {
      "id": "63313b9baff09e0000bcb335",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1664170907,
      "updated": 1664170907
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7d870caff09e00009d2c2c",
      "text": "説明的なリンク: [湖にコップ一杯の水を入れたら水面は上がるか？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1585284876,
      "updated": 1664170921
    },
    {
      "id": "63313b95aff09e0000bcb334",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1664170901,
      "updated": 1664170901
    },
    {
      "id": "63e1bfc9aff09e0000c7365d",
      "text": "[プールにコップ一杯の水を入れる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675739082,
      "updated": 1675739101
    },
    {
      "id": "63e1bfcbaff09e0000c7365e",
      "text": "[正しいけど無益]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675739083,
      "updated": 1675739138
    },
    {
      "id": "63e1c004aff09e0000c73660",
      "text": "[正しいけど愚か]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675739140,
      "updated": 1675739146
    },
    {
      "id": "63e1bffaaff09e0000c7365f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675739131,
      "updated": 1675739131
    },
    {
      "id": "63ede63eaff09e00001842ec",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676535358,
      "updated": 1676535360
    },
    {
      "id": "63ede640aff09e00001842ee",
      "text": "　[ワインに汚水を注ぐたとえ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676535360,
      "updated": 1676535367
    },
    {
      "id": "63ede63faff09e00001842ed",
      "text": "　　このたとえ話に揃えると「樽一杯の汚水にワインをひとさじ入れる、ワインに近いてないといえば誤りだが、ワインに近づいたというのは愚かである」かな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676535360,
      "updated": 1676535460
    },
    {
      "id": "63ede665aff09e00001842ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676535397,
      "updated": 1676535397
    }
  ]
}